WEBVTT

00:19.144 --> 00:21.396
I can’t see anything... but...

00:22.355 --> 00:24.899
I can tell by instinct,
the little guy's in trouble!

00:31.531 --> 00:34.909
The reason I was able to perceive
Tao that one time was...

00:35.493 --> 00:38.329
because blood blurred one of my eyes.

00:39.748 --> 00:43.168
Because I couldn’t see,
I relied on my senses.

00:46.504 --> 00:50.091
One eye gouged out, the other blurred...

00:51.217 --> 00:53.928
I see, now I can’t see anything.

00:55.013 --> 00:58.475
But this time, I can feel it clearly!

01:08.276 --> 01:10.820
You really are the best woman.

01:10.904 --> 01:12.197
I thank you!

01:12.947 --> 01:15.909
This is getting interesting!

02:53.339 --> 02:55.967
In a peaceful world without war,

02:56.050 --> 03:00.346
taking the land with a sword
had long been nothing but a fantasy.

03:00.430 --> 03:05.476
Even so, I kept swinging. Faster, sharper.

03:05.560 --> 03:08.479
Seeking a sword stronger than anyone else.

03:09.522 --> 03:12.483
I aimed for just one thing.

03:13.651 --> 03:16.029
To cut down every powerful foe...

03:19.073 --> 03:20.742
to go beyond this lifetime...

03:21.868 --> 03:23.244
and even into eternity...

03:24.287 --> 03:26.664
and carve my name.

03:37.675 --> 03:40.094
You fucking old man...

03:41.054 --> 03:43.014
Why are you so strong?

03:43.723 --> 03:47.852
You’re thinner and slower than me,
so why?!

03:47.936 --> 03:51.522
Tetsunosuke, you’re greedy.

03:51.606 --> 03:54.400
Because you’re young,
you want to add everything.

03:54.984 --> 04:00.114
You want it thicker,
harder, hotter, faster.

04:00.198 --> 04:03.076
And that’s why you’ve become scattered.

04:03.868 --> 04:06.996
Not everything you eat
becomes part of you.

04:07.080 --> 04:09.082
Eat too much, and it just comes out.

04:09.874 --> 04:12.335
When you’re young, that’s fine, but...

04:12.418 --> 04:14.587
when you get older,
you need to start subtracting,

04:14.671 --> 04:16.422
keep throwing away,

04:16.506 --> 04:19.175
and look closely at what remains.

04:19.259 --> 04:21.594
Because everything will be in there.

04:21.678 --> 04:25.014
Don’t spread out. Go deeper.

04:25.098 --> 04:27.100
When you put it sideways,
it ends up being the same.

04:29.978 --> 04:32.563
You make as little sense
as always, old man.

04:33.189 --> 04:34.232
SAKATA'S TAVERN

04:34.315 --> 04:37.110
Back then, I didn’t understand
my master’s words.

04:37.193 --> 04:38.278
You bastard!

04:38.361 --> 04:40.571
- Where are you going?!
- Hey, are you okay?

04:45.201 --> 04:48.162
That’s why I traveled
all over the country.

04:49.706 --> 04:52.709
But now I get it.

04:52.792 --> 04:57.338
The more you add,
the harder it is to see yourself.

05:04.595 --> 05:06.014
The more you take away...

05:12.645 --> 05:14.230
the clearer it becomes!

05:18.526 --> 05:21.321
Thanks to you, I’ve gotten even stronger.

05:21.404 --> 05:24.198
Amazing, but...

05:24.824 --> 05:26.701
that won’t kill me.

05:27.368 --> 05:29.037
Then as long as I live!

05:29.120 --> 05:30.580
For a long time!

05:31.456 --> 05:33.207
Forever and ever!

05:33.291 --> 05:35.960
I'll keep carving you up!

05:37.378 --> 05:38.838
How romantic!

05:43.551 --> 05:45.136
He's got incredible drive.

05:45.219 --> 05:48.389
But if this turns
into a battle of attrition...

05:50.767 --> 05:52.393
we’ll lose.

05:53.478 --> 05:55.229
Even if we can read Tao,

05:55.313 --> 05:58.399
without the effect of mutual overcoming,
our opponent won't die.

05:58.483 --> 06:00.568
Tao Fa's attribute is "wood."

06:00.651 --> 06:01.527
‎WOOD, FIRE, EARTH, METAL, WATER

06:01.611 --> 06:03.571
With my "metal" I could kill her.

06:03.654 --> 06:06.657
But since I can’t use Tao,
the effect is weak.

06:06.741 --> 06:08.451
If too much time passes,

06:08.534 --> 06:10.661
Gantetsusai will bleed to death.

06:11.245 --> 06:12.455
What should we do?

06:13.414 --> 06:16.584
Mutual generation is a current
that supports the other’s flow.

06:17.418 --> 06:19.128
Mutual overcoming
is a current that blocks it.

06:23.883 --> 06:26.219
What are you doing? Move it, Shorty-mon!

06:26.302 --> 06:28.054
Is this the type of thing you're into?

06:28.137 --> 06:30.640
The reason mutual overcoming
kills a Tensen

06:30.723 --> 06:33.184
is because Tao stops
the Tanden from regenerating.

06:33.267 --> 06:35.520
In other words, right after destruction,

06:35.603 --> 06:38.815
if I'm touching the Tanden and I have
mutual overcoming, the effect is the same!

06:39.816 --> 06:42.318
Keep cutting her up, Tamiya Gantetsusai!

06:42.401 --> 06:43.402
What?

06:43.486 --> 06:45.988
Of course, be careful not to cut me!

06:46.072 --> 06:47.824
That's nothing for an Asaemon!

06:47.907 --> 06:50.076
But is it too much trouble
for the "Sword Dragon"?!

06:53.663 --> 06:54.956
Let’s do it then!

06:59.919 --> 07:03.881
Honestly, with this eye, delicate
swordsmanship is extremely difficult.

07:04.590 --> 07:07.260
At this rate, I’ll cut
the kid down along with her.

07:10.888 --> 07:12.390
Throw away...

07:12.473 --> 07:15.393
Throw away... and look closely...

07:15.476 --> 07:17.687
at what remains.

07:17.770 --> 07:20.523
Because everything will be in there.

07:33.578 --> 07:34.787
Amazing...

07:34.871 --> 07:38.291
See, Shorty-mon? Piece of cake.

07:40.042 --> 07:41.169
Ju Fa...

07:45.756 --> 07:48.634
Without mutual overcoming,
this'll never end.

07:48.718 --> 07:51.179
But we can’t take too much time.

07:52.597 --> 07:54.223
There’s only one thing left.

07:56.392 --> 07:58.311
No, you can't, Brother.

07:59.020 --> 08:00.813
Let’s kill him together.

08:03.191 --> 08:04.317
You're right.

08:04.400 --> 08:06.736
Did you really think

08:06.819 --> 08:09.655
you could bare your fangs
at us and get out alive?

08:09.739 --> 08:12.450
You fools don't think
about what comes next.

08:12.533 --> 08:13.910
What comes next?

08:13.993 --> 08:18.206
If what’s behind us or what’s in front
of us gets in the way, we just crush it.

08:18.289 --> 08:20.583
This guy will get the side.

08:20.666 --> 08:22.335
That'll be enough.

08:24.128 --> 08:27.340
Livestock, at least
on that I agree with you.

08:30.176 --> 08:32.595
The two of us are enough.

08:34.639 --> 08:38.601
Ju Fa, help me!

08:47.693 --> 08:52.365
Sorry, Tao Fa.
I got heated and left you alone.

08:53.616 --> 08:56.911
After all, the two of us must be together.

09:04.627 --> 09:07.964
Let's pulverize them together.

09:15.638 --> 09:20.560
Ju Fa, Tao Fa. You two are one together.

09:22.853 --> 09:25.064
Everyone else is family as well,

09:26.399 --> 09:28.359
but you two are special.

09:30.611 --> 09:32.280
I kind of knew it.

09:38.744 --> 09:42.248
No one else fears the Soshin or Doshi.

09:43.916 --> 09:46.502
They study immortality seriously.

09:48.045 --> 09:50.464
Tao Fa fears the Soshin.

09:50.548 --> 09:52.842
And I don't really like studying.

09:55.344 --> 09:59.265
No one else cares if a comrade gets hurt.

10:01.976 --> 10:04.103
Probably because they won’t die.

10:10.192 --> 10:13.487
But I can't stand it even if Tao Fa
gets just a little scratch.

10:16.073 --> 10:20.745
That's probably because you have
someone who's precious to you, Ju Fa.

10:23.581 --> 10:27.043
You understand your own pain,

10:27.126 --> 10:30.171
but you can only imagine
other people's pain, right?

10:30.838 --> 10:33.758
Because there's someone else,
it makes you think about it.

10:34.925 --> 10:38.012
Imagination is the beginning
of anxiety and kindness.

10:38.804 --> 10:41.766
It's hard to notice
with a body like this, though.

10:41.849 --> 10:45.519
Ju Fa! Everyone's playing over here!

10:46.145 --> 10:47.104
Tao Fa.

10:48.356 --> 10:49.523
Shall we go?

10:50.483 --> 10:52.151
Time is what we have most of.

10:52.234 --> 10:55.655
Let's all take our time
and learn together.

10:57.281 --> 11:00.076
The first abnormality was Rien.

11:00.868 --> 11:05.790
They were wooden people.
Like prototypes of Tensen.

11:06.457 --> 11:08.709
They were made to live outside the castle.

11:09.418 --> 11:12.588
Use them to replenish spent Tao.

11:12.671 --> 11:13.923
Replenish?

11:14.006 --> 11:18.052
You will all now begin
full-scale training.

11:18.135 --> 11:21.680
You were all created
for that purpose to begin with.

11:22.556 --> 11:25.726
Ran practices "Douin."
Mu Dan practices "Shuten."

11:25.810 --> 11:29.814
Gui Fa practices "Shuitsu."
Zhu Jin practices "Taisoku."

11:30.398 --> 11:31.607
And lastly...

11:40.282 --> 11:42.952
Ju Fa and Tao Fa
practice "bedchamber arts."

11:43.035 --> 11:46.705
That’s why you two were raised as a pair.

11:47.289 --> 11:50.084
It’s abrupt, but unavoidable.

11:50.167 --> 11:54.213
Each of you train and teach one another.

11:55.089 --> 11:57.925
The kindness in Rien vanished.

12:02.471 --> 12:05.724
I don’t want to use wooden people.

12:06.559 --> 12:08.978
I start imagining how they feel.

12:19.196 --> 12:21.031
Me too, Tao Fa.

12:21.115 --> 12:24.743
It’s not much, but let’s replenish
Tao from fruit and things like that.

12:27.496 --> 12:29.248
Thank you.

12:29.957 --> 12:34.003
I’m glad I was paired with you, Ju Fa.

12:34.837 --> 12:38.924
A few years later, Mei disappeared
from inside the castle.

12:39.008 --> 12:40.509
No one knew why.

12:41.677 --> 12:45.014
More than anything, no one seemed to care.

12:46.223 --> 12:48.142
The training grew harsher.

12:49.810 --> 12:52.771
And everyone’s senses
became more distorted.

12:55.941 --> 12:58.986
It's okay. I'm with you.

12:59.069 --> 12:59.904
Yeah.

13:00.529 --> 13:02.740
I had to protect Tao Fa's smile.

13:05.117 --> 13:09.663
A hundred years passed, and the animals
brought from the continent died out.

13:10.289 --> 13:11.749
The training continued.

13:12.917 --> 13:16.629
Another 100 years passed.
The village of wooden people collapsed.

13:17.588 --> 13:19.298
The training continued.

13:21.175 --> 13:23.302
How long are we going to keep doing this?!

13:23.385 --> 13:27.097
Soon, not just the wooden people,
but even crops will run out.

13:27.181 --> 13:29.183
What are Rien and the Master thinking?

13:29.934 --> 13:32.436
They must both have their reasons.

13:32.520 --> 13:36.440
If they're concerned about Tao supplies,
we can pull them from outside.

13:36.524 --> 13:39.360
Outside... Humans beyond this place?

13:39.443 --> 13:40.945
What else?

13:41.529 --> 13:46.283
If you don’t like it, then eventually,
Tao will run out, and everyone will die.

13:46.367 --> 13:49.703
Our immortality is only
that good, after all.

13:50.412 --> 13:54.625
To begin with, no matter
how much we train,

13:54.708 --> 13:57.836
we’ll probably never
achieve perfect immortality.

14:01.632 --> 14:05.344
So our training... Tao Fa's suffering...

14:05.427 --> 14:07.137
It was meaningless?!

14:13.060 --> 14:16.272
How can you all still smile?

14:17.147 --> 14:19.525
Have you all really gone mad?

14:20.109 --> 14:23.487
Did endless training make you mad?

14:24.238 --> 14:28.450
Or am I... Are Tao Fa and I
the ones who are crazy?

14:30.327 --> 14:32.872
I have to protect Tao Fa's smile.

14:39.837 --> 14:43.132
What on earth is that, Tao Fa?

14:44.842 --> 14:46.886
It's "bait."

14:47.428 --> 14:50.514
We'll use it to lure people from outside.

14:51.223 --> 14:55.269
In the Master’s homeland, they give
flowers to call people someplace.

14:55.352 --> 14:56.770
Perfect, right?

14:57.396 --> 14:59.481
Well, if we do it a few times,

14:59.565 --> 15:03.277
someone who finds it strange
might come to investigate.

15:03.903 --> 15:07.114
If they come through the floodgate,
they won't be attacked by the sea gods.

15:07.197 --> 15:10.284
Riding the currents,
they'll drift to Japan.

15:10.367 --> 15:12.536
I don’t want to use wooden people.

15:13.245 --> 15:15.539
I start imagining how they feel.

15:16.582 --> 15:19.043
Tao Fa, are you okay with this?

15:19.668 --> 15:20.711
With that...

15:31.639 --> 15:33.766
Totally fine!

15:35.476 --> 15:37.102
Is that strange?

15:51.450 --> 15:55.079
It’s not strange. Of course it isn’t.

15:57.915 --> 16:02.586
Humans are the same as wooden people.
Lower than livestock.

16:02.670 --> 16:04.505
We can use them as much as we want.

16:14.723 --> 16:16.892
We're not crazy.

16:18.519 --> 16:21.939
It's this world that's crazy.

16:34.785 --> 16:38.330
Everything except us is crazy.

16:39.206 --> 16:42.626
Livestock... You livestock...

16:43.460 --> 16:45.879
That's Kishikai...

16:45.963 --> 16:47.923
It fused.

16:48.007 --> 16:50.592
Wings... No, a single wing?

16:50.676 --> 16:53.262
Either way, it should have
trouble moving indoors.

17:00.227 --> 17:01.937
We can't do anything like this!

17:02.021 --> 17:03.397
Huh? What did you say?

17:03.480 --> 17:04.690
Brother!

17:13.073 --> 17:14.950
It can fly damn well with those wings.

17:15.034 --> 17:17.995
Agreed. Structurally impossible.

17:18.620 --> 17:22.332
Misshapen and unnatural.
Yet somehow alluring.

17:22.416 --> 17:25.502
Like "love" itself in its given form.

17:27.421 --> 17:30.841
You’re struggling more than expected
after all that confidence, brothers.

17:30.924 --> 17:33.594
You're next after the monster, old man!

17:33.677 --> 17:36.346
Hey now, I won't let you get ahead of me!

17:36.430 --> 17:40.100
Wait! You’re bleeding too much.
You need treatment!

17:40.184 --> 17:42.102
You think we have time to dawdle?

17:42.186 --> 17:43.979
If I kill the monster...

17:45.147 --> 17:46.273
my name will live on.

17:46.356 --> 17:48.275
You won't keep your life!

17:50.194 --> 17:52.154
Then so be it.

18:09.671 --> 18:11.298
Gantetsusai! Hey!

18:12.424 --> 18:14.593
Are those cottony spores causing this?

18:20.015 --> 18:23.060
Get into cover!
If the spores stick, it's dangerous!

18:27.564 --> 18:29.316
This is bad.

18:31.276 --> 18:32.820
They're endless.

18:33.737 --> 18:34.822
Brother!

18:35.739 --> 18:38.826
I know! But don’t stop me now.

18:39.743 --> 18:40.577
Okay.

18:41.662 --> 18:44.665
It's not like this power
is uncontrollable.

18:44.748 --> 18:46.458
As long as I keep my ego...

19:00.055 --> 19:01.473
Just as I thought.

19:01.557 --> 19:04.518
My "metal" Tao works on Tao Fa’s "wood."

19:04.601 --> 19:06.854
If I can destroy her Tanden,
I can kill her!

19:07.437 --> 19:08.647
But...

19:36.216 --> 19:37.134
Brother!

19:39.261 --> 19:41.763
That huge body moves fast.

19:41.847 --> 19:44.391
And worst of all, it has two Tandens.

19:44.975 --> 19:48.270
Well, well, what happened
to that bravado, Brother?

19:48.353 --> 19:49.730
- Shut up!
- Brother!

19:49.813 --> 19:51.940
Brother, brother, brother, brother!

19:52.024 --> 19:54.526
Okay, okay, everyone calm themselves down.

19:55.319 --> 19:59.114
That monster isn't something
an individual sword can handle.

19:59.198 --> 20:01.033
We’ll have to cooperate,
even if we don't like it.

20:01.116 --> 20:03.452
Team up with this guy? You’re joking.

20:03.535 --> 20:05.787
I’ll pass. Especially with an injured guy.

20:05.871 --> 20:09.708
Rude little brat, aren't you?
I’m your brother’s mentor, you know.

20:09.791 --> 20:12.211
He's not a brat!
And I don’t owe you anything!

20:12.294 --> 20:13.170
You heard him.

20:13.253 --> 20:15.923
Shall we discipline
both brothers together?

20:16.006 --> 20:19.051
Shut up, idiot!

20:26.099 --> 20:28.518
Our immediate enemy is that monster.

20:30.187 --> 20:33.023
If you want to kill
each other, do it after.

20:34.816 --> 20:37.819
If you drag us down, I'll kill you.

20:37.903 --> 20:39.988
That’s my line.

20:40.656 --> 20:42.783
All right, let's do this.

20:42.866 --> 20:44.826
I'm still treating your wound.

20:44.910 --> 20:47.371
How did you put up with someone like this?

20:47.454 --> 20:49.957
You’re the one who said to wait,
aren't you, Brother?

20:51.083 --> 20:52.542
Well then...

20:53.210 --> 20:55.045
Let's exterminate this demon!

22:30.098 --> 22:33.977
How long did that "Doshi" or whatever
say it'd be till we got

22:34.061 --> 22:35.520
to that "Horai" place?

22:35.604 --> 22:37.939
About 20 miles.
We'll get there before dawn.

22:38.023 --> 22:39.066
What?!

22:39.149 --> 22:41.610
Isn’t that a bit extreme?

22:41.693 --> 22:44.946
They do say "a ninja runs
100 miles a day," but...

22:45.030 --> 22:47.866
But we're samurai,
and we don't even have horses.

22:49.242 --> 22:51.745
Then... we’ll use the horse flute.

22:52.788 --> 22:53.872
Horse flute?

22:53.955 --> 22:57.334
Huh? No, no way. You’re serious?

22:57.417 --> 23:00.879
Of course. I learned how to use it
after "interrogating" a Doshi.

23:00.962 --> 23:04.216
No, no... You’re completely unhinged.

23:04.299 --> 23:05.133
- Stop--
- Shugen.

23:05.217 --> 23:08.303
The lower ninja who was
searching the area has returned.

23:08.804 --> 23:12.265
They recovered items believed
to belong to those who landed ashore.

23:12.349 --> 23:13.767
Please inspect them.

23:16.812 --> 23:19.773
Tenza... Genji...

23:19.856 --> 23:23.652
That's... It can't be... Brother!

23:24.319 --> 23:25.779
Genji!

23:25.862 --> 23:28.365
Judging from the condition of the bodies,

23:28.448 --> 23:30.784
it seems some were killed by criminals.

23:33.120 --> 23:35.664
There’s no time to lose.

23:35.747 --> 23:38.750
We'll go to Horai at once
and find our comrades.

23:38.834 --> 23:41.294
Tensen... criminals...

23:41.920 --> 23:43.130
I’ll kill all of them!

23:43.630 --> 23:45.465
In that case, Shugen...

23:48.510 --> 23:50.637
This is the cave we talked about.

23:51.930 --> 23:53.807
Please use the horse flute.

23:54.432 --> 23:55.934
What's that flute?

23:56.017 --> 23:57.561
You don't remember?

23:57.644 --> 24:00.063
It's the flute that controls monsters.

24:03.483 --> 24:06.444
That cave is the monsters' lair.

24:08.488 --> 24:11.074
- You don't mean...
- I mean exactly that.

24:11.158 --> 24:13.076
I told you, didn’t I?

24:14.035 --> 24:16.955
Our Shugen has completely lost it.

24:22.043 --> 24:24.171
Everyone, we're coming!

24:24.254 --> 24:25.964
‎Subtitle translation by: Maslin Friedman
